<br />
That is how we handle it in Germany. All males are required to serve for 10 months in the army OR do some social service (unless you have two older brothers who already served in the army or you're not fit for any physical labor etc). 
<br />

<br />
Anyway, in the end the majority of germans males is serving or doing some social work for at least 10 months in his life. Can't say that this is a bad thing. You are thaught what duty, respect and loyality means <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
