				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Draft - no
<br />

<br />
If my little brother or sister came back in a body bag because they were drafted, I wouldn't be able to handle it.  No way should my siblings be forced to die in a war that we didn't want.  As for serving our country, we do it every day-- so that line doesn't work either.
<br />

<br />
I would say if a draft goes into effect, the current administration should have to send their children into war (into a position that would be normally assigned if their parents weren't politically powerful).  After all, fair is fair.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1023548" target=_blank>Aderyn- cleric bot</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.hneguild.com" target=_blank>Heaven and Earth</a>
<br />
Saryrn</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
